<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <!-- Bootstrap -->
    <link
      rel="stylesheet"
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@4.6.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
    />
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/jquery@3.7.1/dist/jquery.slim.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/popper.js@1.16.1/dist/umd/popper.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@4.6.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>

    <!-- Custom CSS -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/css/main.css" />
    <title>Privacy Policy</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <header>
      <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-xl nav-container">
        <!-- Brand -->
        <a class="navbar-brand" href="/">
          <img src="/images/logo.png" alt="logo" />
        </a>

        <button
          class="navbar-toggler"
          type="button"
          data-toggle="collapse"
          data-target="#collapsibleNavbar"
        >
          <span class="navbar-toggler-icon">
            <img src="/images/hamburger-menu.png" alt="hamburger-menu" />
          </span>
        </button>

        <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="collapsibleNavbar">
          <ul class="navbar-nav">
            <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="/recipes">Recipes</a></li>

            <li class="nav-item dropdown">
              <% if (userId) { %>
                <a class="nav-link dropdown-toggle" href="#" data-toggle="dropdown">
                  My Account
                </a>
                <div class="dropdown-menu">
                  <a class="dropdown-item" href="/recipes/create-recipe">Create New Recipe</a>
                  <a class="dropdown-item" href="/profile">My Profile</a>
                  <a class="dropdown-item" href="/profile/edit-profile">My Recipes</a>
                  <a class="dropdown-item" href="/profile/edit-profile">Saved Recipes</a>
                  <form action="/users/logout" method="POST">
                    <button class="dropdown-item" type="submit">Logout</button>
                  </form>
                </div>
              <% } else { %>
                <li class="nav-item">
                  <a class="nav-link" href="/users/login">Login / Signup</a>
                </li>
              <% } %>
            </li>

            <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="/about">About Us</a></li>

            <li>
              <form class="form-inline" action="/recipes/search" method="GET">
                 <input class="form-control mr-sm-2" type="text" placeholder="Search" name="query" />
              </form>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </nav>
    </header>

    <main class="container mt-5">
      <h2 class="text-center">Privacy Policy</h2>
      <hr />

      <section>
        <h4>1. Introduction</h4>
        <p>
          Welcome to Swaply. Your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and share your information when you use our website.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h4>2. Information We Collect</h4>
        <p>We may collect the following types of information:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Personal details (e.g., name, email, username) when you sign up.</li>
          <li>Recipe submissions and comments you make on our platform.</li>
          <li>Usage data including your browsing habits on our site.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h4>3. How We Use Your Information</h4>
        <p>We use your information to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Provide and personalize our services.</li>
          <li>Communicate with you regarding updates or support.</li>
          <li>Improve our platform and enhance user experience.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h4>4. Data Protection</h4>
        <p>
          We implement security measures to protect your personal data. However, no online platform is 100% secure, so we encourage users to take necessary precautions.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h4>5. Sharing of Information</h4>
        <p>We do not sell or rent your personal information. However, we may share it with:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Service providers that help us operate our platform.</li>
          <li>Authorities if required by law or to prevent fraud.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h4>6. Your Rights</h4>
        <p>You have the right to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Access and update your personal information.</li>
          <li>Request deletion of your account.</li>
          <li>Opt-out of marketing emails.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h4>7. Changes to this Policy</h4>
        <p>
          We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We encourage you to review it regularly for any changes.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h4>8. Contact Us</h4>
        <p>
          If you have any questions regarding our Privacy Policy, please contact us at <a href="mailto:support@swaply.com">support@swaply.com</a>.
        </p>
      </section>
    </main>

    <!-- FOOTER -->
    <footer class="footer mt-5 py-3">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row text-center text-md-left">
          <!-- Left Section: Follow Us -->
          <div class="col-md-4">
            <h6><u>Follow Us</u></h6>
            <a href="https://facebook.com" target="_blank">
              <img src="/images/facebookicon.png" alt="Facebook" width="24" />
            </a>
            <a href="https://instagram.com" target="_blank">
              <img src="/images/instaicon.png" alt="Instagram" width="24" />
            </a>
          </div>

          <!-- Center Section: Copyright -->
          <div class="col-md-4 text-md-center">
            <p>Â© 2024 Swaply. All Rights Reserved.</p>
          </div>

          <!-- Right Section: Privacy Policy & Terms -->
          <div class="col-md-4 text-md-right">
            <a href="/privacy-policy" class="mr-3">Privacy Policy</a>
            <a href="/terms-and-conditions">Terms and Conditions</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
